----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
------------------------------- TurtleKit 3.0.0.4 (alpha-4)-----------------------
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Changes:
	- upgrading to MaDKit 5.0.5.1
	- upgrading to JCuda 6.5
	- Various changes : still alpha style
	
2. Bug fix:
	- the statesPerSecond viewer now works in every contexts.
	- various bug fixes

3. API changes:
	~ name changed : turtlekit.viewer.AbstractViewer -> turtlekit.viewer.AbstractGridViewer
	~ name changed : turtlekit.viewer.AbstractChartViewer -> turtlekit.viewer.AbstractObserver
	+ turtlekit.kernel.TKEnvironment.createTurtle(Turtle, double, double)
	


